  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ad tappe Dahwidam\nSluddinahts un faZZihts:\nRangi/ tee Wilisteri kar-\nro prett Kegilu / un aplaupa tohs\nKlohnus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad waizaja Dahwids to\nKUNGU / un faZZija: Buhs\nman eet / un tohs Wilisterus\nfaut? un tas KUNGS faZZija\nus Dahwidu: Eij/ jo tu kausi\ntohs Wilisterus / un iṣglahbſi\nKegilu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Dahwida Wihrī faZ-\nziia us to : Diedsi/ mehs bih-\nſtanees ſcheit eekſch Juha/ ka\nwarretum mehs us Kegilu eet/\nprett to Wilisteru Kara-Pulkeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad waizaja Dahwids-at-\nkat to KUNGU/ un tas KUNGS\natbildeja tam/ un faZZija: Zelleeß/\nno-eij us Kegilu / jo es dohnu\ntohs Wilisterus tawa Rohkā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nogahje Dahwids ar\nfaweem Wihrēem us Kegilu/un\nkarroja prett teem Wilistereem /\nun atsdsinne winnu Lohpus / un\nkawe no teem (dauds) ar leelu\nRaufchanu. Ta atpestija Dah-\nwids tohs Eedsihwotajus no\nKegitas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo kad Abjatars Akimeleka\nDehls pee Dahwida behdse uhs\nKegilu / tad nonahze wiṣch ar\nto Gewodu fawa Rohkā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu Saulam tapve\nfluddinahts/ka Dahwids uhs Re\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fuſauze Sauls toh\nLandis Karra/ ka tee no-eetu u\nKegilu / Dahwidu ar fawee\nWihrēem apſehſt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu Dahwids nomanija\nka Sauls ſcho Launumu pre\nwinnu fleppeni bij apſehmis\nfaZZija wiṣch us to Preesteri Al\njataru: Neſs to Gewodu fchuṛ\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Dahwids faZZija\nKUNGS Israēta Deews/tan\nKalps irr to Sławu dsirdejs /\nSauls mekle us Kegilu nahkt/\nPilsfahtu famaitaht manis del\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Arrig jafchu tee Namne\nki no Kegilaß mannt nodohs wi\nna Rohkā? arrig arridsan Sau-\nleija nahks / itt ka taws Kal-\ndsirdejs ? KUNGS Israē-\nDeews / stahsti jelle to tawa\nKalpam.Tad faZZija tas KUNG\nWiṣch nonahks leija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz faZZija Dahwids\nNodohs tad tee Namneeki\nKegilaß mann un mannis Wi-\nrus Saula Rohkā? tad faZZi-\ntas KUNGS: Tee nodohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad zehlehs Dahwids\nfaweem Wihrēem/ peez fetchſin\nWihrēem/ un iṣgahje no Kegila\nun gahje kur warredami. Un\nSaulam fluddinahts tappe /\nDahwids no Kegilaß bij aisbe-\ndsie/tad palikfe wiṣch ne iṣgahj\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Dahwids mitte Tu\n"
    }
  ],
